      "module_path": "tddd::baseline_graph_renderer_adapter",
      "docs": "Infrastructure adapter implementing BaselineGraphRenderer port. Reads .harness/config/baseline-graph-style.toml (Reality View dedicated style config, Decision L / IN-04). Produces depth-1 overview (render_overview) and all depth-2 cluster files (render_clusters) for rustdoc_types::Crate input. render_clusters owns the full cluster-enumeration pipeline: it filters krate.paths to local-crate items only (crate_id == 0), derives cluster keys per IN-14/IN-15, and returns Vec<ClusterRender>. No syn dependency — rustdoc already parses types (Decision E note / CN-03). Style config DTO types are private. Symmetric to ContractMapRendererAdapter. (IN-02 / IN-14 / IN-15 / AC-02 / AC-15 / CN-02)",
